Package: naruto
Type: Package
Title: An Interface to the Naruto Database API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ernest", "Guevarra", 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4887-4415"), 
    email = "ernest@guevarra.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The NarutoDB API <https://narutodb.xyz/api> offers a comprehensive 
    database featuring all the characters, clans, villages, kekkei genkai, 
    tailed beasts, teams, akatsuki, and rara members from the renowned anime and 
    manga series *Naruto*. The API provides detailed information on each 
    character, including their names, appearances, personalities, jutsus, and 
    ninja tools. This package interfaces with the NarutoDB API through R.
